# Ignore heavy training artifacts by default.
**/artifacts/**

# Keep only result reports, metrics, and generated figures.
!**/artifacts/**/
!**/artifacts/**/reports/
!**/artifacts/**/reports/**
!**/artifacts/**/reports/**/*.md
!**/artifacts/**/reports/**/*.json
!**/artifacts/**/reports/**/*.png
!**/artifacts/**/reports/**/*.jpg
!**/artifacts/**/reports/**/*.jpeg
!**/artifacts/**/reports/**/*.csv
